        },
        "text_HcdW73": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>1. Does not cover if you just decide to give up because it is hard or painful.<br/></strong>We tell everyone that this process is hard upfront.  You need to be mentally prepared for it.  So this is not a reason for a refund.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_QVEgqY": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>2. Does not cover if you just show up one day and decided it didn't work<br/></strong>You need to demonstrate that you are doing the process as we prescribe it. This can be via the journal or if you send Ken updates via Skool DM's with challenges you are facing.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_XF74BH": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>3. Does not cover if it's not going fast enough for you.<br/></strong>This process takes time and you need to be in it for the long game. Expecting to correct your profile or achieve massive changes in facial symmetry in a month is not realistic.</p>"
          }
        }
